{
  "id": "adv_bond_ski_01_02",
  "title": "白石沙季2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、千紗\nロケの下見に付き合ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Chisa\nFor joining me on the site visit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.033333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、私も植物園って社会科見学以来だし\n凄く楽しいよ。見てるだけで癒やされちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I haven't been to a botanical garden since a school trip\nIt's really fun. Just watching it makes me feel relaxed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.23333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お姉ちゃん、見て！　ハエトリグサがあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Saki-chan‚ look! There's a venus flytrap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.53333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あら、知ってるのね\n北アメリカ原産の、有名な食虫植物よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you knew it\nA famous carnivorous plant native to North America",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "葉の内側についた毛に触れると\nパクッて葉が閉じて、虫を捕まえるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When an insect touches the bristles on the inside of the leaves‚\nthe leaves snap shut‚ trapping it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.866666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうなんだ～。昔観たホラー映画で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see~. There was a really big one in a horror movie",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0000002544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく大きいのが出てきてね。その時の餌は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw a long time ago. The prey at that time was――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0999982198
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗？\nなんとなく分かったから、それくらいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Chisa?\nI feel like I know somehow‚ until there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5333335877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あそこには、ウツボカズラがあるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! There're monkey cups over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "壺型の葉っぱが特徴的な植物よね。虫を捕まえる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a plant with distinctive pot-shaped leaves. They are like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4333335877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "罠になっていて、中には消化液が溜まっているの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "traps for catching insects‚ and the inside contain digestive juices",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "土に栄養が少ない場所でも、虫を栄養にして\n生きていけるように進化した、と言われているけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is said that‚ they evolved to survive in places\nwhere the soil is poor in nutrients by feeding on insects…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昔、テレビでやってたホラー系のドラマで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A long time ago‚ a really big one appeared",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2000002544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく大きいのが出てきたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in a horror drama on TV~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、そういう知識なのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ it's that kind of knowledge…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6333335877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でもお姉ちゃん、植物に詳しいんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Saki-chan‚ you know a lot about plants",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.2666684469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "これなら、下見に来なくても大丈夫だったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ wouldn't it have been okay not to come for a site visit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、これはあくまで事前に調べてきたことだから\nそれに、実際に来た方が、本番をイメージしやすいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this is because I researched it in advance\nAlso‚ it's easier to think of it as a live when it actually comes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わぁ、さすがお姉ちゃん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ Saki-chan…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6333371481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.6333371481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "今度のロケ、絶対うまくいくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This show‚ will definitely go well",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう。あ、見て、あそこにあるのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you. Oh‚ look‚ that thing over there",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9333371481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.9333371481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "キンシャチサボテンって言って――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is called a golden barrel cactus――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（やっぱりお姉ちゃんって凄いな～。オフの日も）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I knew‚ Saki-chan is amazing~. Even on her day off‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5000038148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.5000038148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "（こうしてお仕事のために頑張って……って、あれ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（she working so hard for work… wait‚ huh?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0875086388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あそこに見えてる木ですか？　あれはタコノキですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that the tree you see over there? That's a pandanus tree",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5666704815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.5666704815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい、根がタコの足みたいに分かれているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ the roots are split like octopus tentacles",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、なんでしょう？　サガリバナの特徴、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ what is it? What are the characteristics of Barringtonia?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666704815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7666704815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、とっても面白いんですよ。幻の花と呼ばれていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ this is really fun. It's called the phantom flower",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7428349218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
